title.narrative: KENYA: NATIONAL URBAN TRANSPORT IMPROVEMENT PROJECT

description.narrative: The Project Development Objectives (PDO) are to: (a) improve the efficiency of road transport along the northern corridor; (b) improve the institutional capacity and arrangements in the urban transport sub sector; and (c) promote the private sector participation in the operation, financing and management of transport systems.
